
to build image:

run maven build:
mvn clean package

run command:
docker build -t kevbob/webtest --build-arg JAR_TO_COPY=target/webtest-*.jar .

-t is a repository and name for the build (a tag)

docker images now lists the  image kevbob/webtest:latest

start docker image and specify zookeeper connection and spring profiles
q
docker run -e SPRING_CLOUD_ZOOKEEPER_CONNECT_STRING=172.17.0.2:2181 -e SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=dev foo


zookeeper properties:
application       <-- applicable to all apps (thing globals)
application,dev   <-- applicable to all apps in dev environment
webtest         <-- empty node
webtest/prop1   <-- contains string value
webtest,dev     <-- empty node
webtest,dev/prop1     <-- contains string value, overrides app value
webtest,dev/prop2     <-- new value, no default

props can be set at app or app,environment level

environment properties override 
